Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I received a complaint from\NChairman Kiel about the delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It came directly to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He was pretty upset.\NHe even hinted at dismissing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Adam is proceeding well,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Eva Project has begun work\Non the dummy plugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What do the old men of Seele\Nhave to complain about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The all-important Human Instrumentality Project\Nis behind schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All the projects are linked.\NThere are no problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Including Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what should we do about that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll leave him to his own devices.\NThe same with the Marduk Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose we'll let him work to our purposes\Nfor a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:24.66,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(966.136,681.75)}KYOTO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What started here, sixteen years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:47.77,Title Cards,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,645)}{\fs70}EPISODE 15\N{\fs90}LIES AND SILENCE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, so it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shannon Bio, a chemical firm\Nfunded from overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been here for nine years,\Nbut it also hasn't changed in nine years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Marduk Institute has\N108 affiliated companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,106 of them turned out to be\Ndummy corporations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the 107th?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the corporate registration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to take a look\Nat the board of directors, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:22.01,Neutral Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1020.083,268)\c&H4B4B4B&}Gendo Ikari
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:22.01,Neutral Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(998.053,402)\c&H4B4B4B&}Kouzou Fuyutsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:22.01,Neutral Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(986.036,528)\c&H4B4B4B&}Kiel Lorenz
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So you already knew about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The names are all familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Marduk Institute is supposed to be\Nan advisory body
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,controlled by the Human Instrumentality\NCommittee to select Eva pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What it really does is not clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your duty is to investigate Nerv.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting involved in the Marduk Institute\Nis a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm the type that has to see\Neverything for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, this is Kaji. I'm out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave your name and message.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, Mr. Kaji! Don't touch me, you pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, tomorrow's Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So I called Mr. Kaji, thinking that I'd get him\Nto take me out somewhere, but he's not in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always out lately, no matter when I call.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you're free tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Regrettably, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I have a little favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! A date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend of my big sister Kodama
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is insisting that I introduce you to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU need to get to it and clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Necrosis operation complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Graph measurement complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to wear tomorrow?\NSynch rate is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, to the wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wore the pink suit for Kiyomi's wedding,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and the dark blue dress for Kotoko's\Njust the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the orange one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't worn that one lately, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's a reason for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too tight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I get a new one on the way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an extra expense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been invited to so many weddings lately,\Nthe cost of all the gifts is starting to add up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's just rushing to get married\Nbefore they're thirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No one wants to be the last one still single.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, you three.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All these stupid tests are boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Shinji looks even more\Ndowncast than usual today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because of tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, I have to see my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I talk to him about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I once saw you\Ntalking happily with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, what kind of person is my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been looking at me all afternoon\Nbecause you wanted to ask me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When we were cleaning today,\Nyou were wringing out the cloth, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you did it was like a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was like a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you'd be really good\Nat being a housewife, Ayanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:59.10,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you mean? You're the one\Nthat wanted to break up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:03.69,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was wrong. I wasn't thinking back then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better go to bed.\NAren't you going on a date tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:05.82,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you saying at this late date?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, with a hunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:09.61,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know about you,\Nbut I'm a different person now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's right, let me use\Nyour lavender perfume!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:12.11,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I still love you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, cheapskate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:15.62,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time and people are two things that can't be\Nturned back to the way they were!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not for kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Shinji in his room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:18.00,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can never go back to the way I was!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been in there since he got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.83,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I really do still love you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like he doesn't want to see his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:22.33,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm telling you, it's impossible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If he doesn't want to, he should just say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand the Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:27.88,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It took me three years to forget you! It's too late!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not that he doesn't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm opening the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared? Of seeing\Nyour father by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:07:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't keep running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you take that step forward,\Nnothing will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll begin to realize,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,after that first step, it's just as important\Nto keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, go see him tomorrow\Nwith your chin held high,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,because you'll be seeing your mother too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you bought a new dress for tomorrow,\Ndidn't you? Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you want to see?\NIt was expensive, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Taste is more important than price.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got that down pat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you pick based on Mr. Kaji's\Ntaste and stuff after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I think not. Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:41.12,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(972.273,681.75)}NEXT DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,See you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Place three bags in your heart...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Red, blue, and yellow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let us proceed with the reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:58.22,Neutral Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000100&\pos(733.686,495)}Mr. Ryoji Kaji
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot has never been on time\Nin his entire life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,For your dates, you mean?\NHe's always on time for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you two! You look\Neven more beautiful today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't get off work in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As if you're not puttering\Naround the office all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I care, but couldn't you have done\Nsomething about that stubble?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, your necktie is crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You two act like you're married.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good to me, Ritchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell I'd take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been three years since the last time\Nwe came here together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran away then,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and haven't been back since.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It just hasn't sunk in that Mother is resting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even remember her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Man survives by forgetting his memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but there are some things\Na man should never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui taught me about the irreplaceable things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I come here to confirm that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no pictures of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There are none left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This grave is just a decoration too.\NThere's no corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the teacher was right.\NYou threw them all away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep everything in my heart.\NThat is enough for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time. I'm leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm glad I got to talk to you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad! I didn't know you played.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been studying since I was five,\Nand this is all I can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't really have any talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Perseverance is power. I'm a little impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I started studying because\Nmy teacher told me to,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so I could have quit anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did you keep going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because nobody told me to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have known!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You came back early.\NI thought you'd have dinner too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He was just so boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, while he was waiting in line\Nfor the roller coaster, I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't seem too nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, Mr. Kaji is the only real man around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you saying after all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ducking out to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ditch me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,High heels...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How many years has it been since\Nthe three of us last drank together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Misato drinking too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She's acting a little giddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And you drink some more to\Nkeep your high spirits in check.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Or vice versa, today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,As someone who lived with her,\Nyour words carry the weight of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I did live with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but that was before she started\Nwearing heels and things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It was unimaginable when\Nwe were back in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a brat too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:13:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't really sharing a life.\NIt was just living together, playing house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Reality isn't that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, here. A cat souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My, thank you. You're very thorough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Only with the ladies.\NWhen it comes to work, I'm sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I somehow doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What about for Misato?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I make a point of not fighting\Nwhen I can't win the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you have a chance at victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I make a point of not talking about myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi's sure taking a long time.\NMaybe she's fixing her make-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing in Kyoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's from Matsushiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use playing dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fingers will get burned if you\Nget involved in this too deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the advice of a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take it seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but if I have to get burned, I'd rather be burned\Nwhile playing with fire along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I go buy you some fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed, have you, you player?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I've changed. To live is to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Homeostasis and transistasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:13:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,One is a force for the status quo,\Nand the other's a force for change.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A living thing is something that has\Nboth of these conflicting qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Like men and women.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be leaving now.\NI've still got some work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shin? It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm drinking with Kaji right now.\NRight, we're on the third after-party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... Okay, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it Misato?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she said she'll be late,\Nso don't wait up for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Don't tell me she's coming back\Nin the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, she's with Mr. Kaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you, stupid? That's WHY!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be throwing up at your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry I'm that age.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we're both that age.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wearing heels now, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Time's really flown.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shave that stubble off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll walk the rest of the way. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaji, do you think I've changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You've become more beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that I insisted on\Nbreaking up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When I said I fell in love with somebody else,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that was a lie. Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that I realized
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you were like my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That I wanted a man like my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When I realized that, I was afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was desperately afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Of being with you, Kaji...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Of being a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was afraid of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I hated my father, but fell in love\Nwith someone just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I chose Nerv, intending to\Nmake a clean break with the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But even that was an organization\Nthat Father used to belong to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I've been fooling myself\Nby taking revenge against the Angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That was your decision, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to apologize to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that wasn't a decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Running away from the snare of my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just like Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry. Telling you all this now\Nbecause I drank too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm such a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no right to tell Shinji anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, I'm an underhanded woman\Nthat just clings to men when it suits me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Even back then, I may have just been using you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinji, do you want to kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A kiss. A kiss? You've never kissed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're bored?! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to kiss a girl on\Nthe anniversary of your mom's death?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Afraid she may be watching you from Heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared of a little kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You brushed your teeth, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't breathe, because it tickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely not something to do to kill time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, here we are. Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you stay with us, Kaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be laughed at if I went to work in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, c'mon, Mr. Kaji...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He smelled of lavender...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, 'night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You look down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I kissed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let me call the girl's roll. Ayanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:55.42,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(966.136,686.25)}NEXT DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ayanami's absent again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:03.76,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,NERV HEADQUARTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:05.26,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,DEEP UNDERGROUND FACILITY\NCENTRAL AREA
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:06.26,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,CENTRAL DOGMA
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.41,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(943.636,715.5)}2008 METERS UNDERGROUND
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:31.20,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964.091,666)}TERMINAL DOGMA
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, how's your hangover?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finally sober now, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this your day job, or your side job?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder which?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryoji Kaji of Special Duty Organization Nerv's\NSpecial Inspection Department...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:21:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, Ryoji Kaji of the Investigation Department\Nof the Japanese Ministry of Home Affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So you know all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate Nerv.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this an order from Commander Ikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My own discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep doing this other job, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Ikari is using me.\NI can still keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I will apologize for hiding it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call it even in thanks for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks very much, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The Commander and Ritchan are hiding\Nthings from you too, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is the origin and linchpin of\Neverything since the Second Impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Adam? The First Angel is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.87,0:21:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nerv is deeper in this than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:00.59,TBC Card,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1542.045,760)}TO BE CONTINUED
