Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The puffed-up Shinji gets swallowed\Nin a Sea of Dirac.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The short amount of time left to him\Nteaches him the meaning of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: "The Sickness Unto Death, And..."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.20,0:23:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,More fan service next time!
